commentable_entity.ask: Replace Amber Heard in upcoming movie "Into the Fire"
commentable_entity.title: Replace Amber Heard in upcoming movie "Into the Fire"
commentable_entity.description:
Amber Heard testified on 05/16/22 that her role in the second Aquaman movie had been reduced and she "fought really hard to stay in the movie".   As of the same date (05/16/22), the petition to have her removed had reached 4.2 million signatures.  This is evidence that our voices are being heard, but we should not give up on having her entirely from the movie.  (She will still make $2 million plus royalties!)

I think Amber should ALSO be replaced in the upcoming supernatural thriller Into the Fire!  Amber has repeatedly lied on Johnny causing him to lose his career.  It's only right that she experience the consequences of her actions in the same manner.  The woman manipulated our legal system and the measures it has in place to protect those who are REAL victims of violence.  Amber is a disgusting person and I would prefer to never see or hear her again.  I sure won't pay to.  Thank you!
